  "antiDriftRules": [
    "Manifests may only reference ids in coarseSceneComponents or controlledFinePieces.",
    "scene_type must map to the locked coarse component in template.lock.json.",
    "Fine pieces may only appear under their declared parent component.",
    "Opening and ending presenter scenes must keep the face visible; no opaque central card may cover the face.",
    "ScreenWithPip allows exactly one circular PIP helper and no decorative second empty circle.",
    "SplitTextPresenter must use accepted split variables and right presenter frame; it must not use a circular PIP as the main presenter.",
